China ta sanar da cewa akwai karuwar kashi 14% a cikin adadin 'yan kasa da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce cutar ta kama mutane fiye da 820,000 a kasar.
An sanar da sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 a rabin rabin shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in sun bazu ta hanyar jima'i, canji daga yanayin da ya kasance.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta bazu cikin sassa na kasar Sin, sakamakon kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar kwayar cutar.
Amma an samu raguwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ta HIV a wannan hanyar kuma yanzu ba a samun kowa a wannan hanyar, in ji jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, shekara shekara, adadin mutanen da suke da HIV da AIDS yana ƙaruwa zuwa 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i lamari ne da ya zama ruwan dare a cikin 'yan luwadi, gay, bisexual da transgender (LGBT) na kasar Sin.
An soke yin luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana cewa ana nuna wa al'ummar LADT wariya.
Saboda ra'ayin da ya sa mutane suke son yin jima'i, wasu bincike sun nuna cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin yaduwar cutar ta faru ne daga kariya ta jima'i, wacce take da rauni a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magungunan cutar HIV domin magance matsalar.
