Wanda ya kirkiro sabuwar yanar gizo na duniya yana da shirin kaddamar da sabuwar yanar gizo domin kalubalanci Google da Facebook.
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, zai fara sabon kamfani, wanda zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin daga sanannen masanin fasaha, Inrupt, shine kamfanin da ke gina Berners-Lee's open source platform, Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su, da kuma mutanen da za a ba su damar samun damar wannan bayanin.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee, a cikin abin dariya, ya ambata cewa burin Inrupt shine dandalin duniya.
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu",in ji shi game da shirin.
