Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji "bacin rai" na rashin jin daɗin jima'i.
Tom Daley, dan wasan Olympic, ya ce ya ji cewa ba shi da kyau a lokacin da yake girma saboda rashin jin daɗin jima'i - amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don ci gaba.
Mutumin mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har ya tafi makarantar sakandare cewa ba kowa bane kamar ni.
Da yake magana a kan shirin farko na Desert Island Discs a Radio 4, wanda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin gays don ba da bege ga wasu.
