Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya kuma rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane sama da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai a Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya lalata garuruwan da ke kusa da shi kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai saukin kai ta afkawa karamar hukuma Pidie Jaya a Aceh. Ta lalata kuma ta girgiza mutanen da suka tuna da tarkacen da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
